msgctxt "seo_title"
msgid "Sign up for Mozilla Foundation updates"
msgstr "Bleiben Sie mit der Mozilla Foundation auf dem Laufenden"

msgctxt "search_description"
msgid "By joining Mozilla Foundation’s community, you’re joining a movement that is making good tech the default. Get involved by signing up for our latest updates."
msgstr "Als Mitglied unserer Community schließen Sie sich einer Bewegung an, die gute Technologie zur Norm machen will. Werden Sie aktiv und melden Sie sich für aktuelle News und Updates an."

msgctxt "title"
msgid "Sign up for Mozilla Foundation updates"
msgstr "Bleiben Sie mit der Mozilla Foundation auf dem Laufenden"

msgctxt "body.907fba92-9b64-451a-95ef-5394d2a84293.image.alt_text"
msgid "people-2-592x296@2x"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.39046206-50e5-4195-9691-6b6d7b0d9aa0"
msgid ""
"The Internet is built by people like you. By joining our community, you’re joining a movement that is making good tech the default. Together we’ll advance trustworthy technology, digital rights, and"
" stand for an Internet that lifts us all."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.39046206-50e5-4195-9691-6b6d7b0d9aa0"
msgid "If you care about the future of the Internet, we hope you’ll sign up for our newsletter."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "header"
msgid "Sign up for Mozilla Foundation updates"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "signed_header"
msgid "Thank you for signing up!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "signed_donation_question"
msgid "Would you like to support our work with a donation?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "signed_body"
msgid "A better Internet starts with you. When you make a donation today it will help shape a better technology future that is good for everyone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "share_header"
msgid "Share this with your friends and family"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "share_body"
msgid ""
"Mozilla Foundation is a non-profit building a better tech future – powered by people, open by design, and fueled by imagination. Can you ask your family and friends to sign up to join the Mozilla "
"Foundation community?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "thank_you_header"
msgid "Thank you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "thank_you_body"
msgid "Together we have the power to make good on the promise of the Internet. Thank you for joining our global movement to shape the future of technology."
msgstr ""
